  "Supply, Warehousing, Output, Transportation": "",
  "Sales, Wealth, Operations, Technology": "",
  "SWOT analysis is a strategic framework examining internal Strengths and Weaknesses, and external Opportunities and Threats, to help businesses assess their competitive position and plan accordingly.": "",
