  "A plan that ensures a business can continue operating or quickly recover after a major disruption": "",
  "A plan for selling the business to a new owner": "",
  "Business continuity planning involves creating procedures and systems that allow a business to maintain essential functions during and after a disaster, cyberattack, or other major disruption.": "",
